| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2956 — Recovery Inhibition (vicesociety)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 989c96d5-2c05-5783-ab39-e717070808d8"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
